item.title: He is Exalted the King is Exalted on High
item.description: He is exalted The King is exalted on high, I will praise Him, He is exalted, Forever exalted, And I will praise His name! He is the Lord, Forever His truth shall reign. Heaven and earth, Rejoice in His holy name, He is exalted, The King is exalted on high!
